<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٧٢٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6333">مَكِّيُّ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6657">هَاشِمُ بْنُ هَاشِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3070">عَامِرِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2289">أَبِيهِ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَقَدْ رَأَيْتُنِي وَأَنَا ثُلُثُ الْإِسْلَامِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>